original: Lundgren, Gudmar Fredrik, komminister, Fröskog, f. 23/6/10 i Högbo, Gävleb. 1., av fd. kontr :prost Johan L. o. Signe Holmquist. G. 40 m. Gunborg Ubrant. Barn: Gudmar f. 40, Ulf 43, Torbjörn 46. — Stud:ex. i Karlstad 31, teol. fil. ex. 33, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Karlstads stift 37. Varit pastiadj. i Köla o. Nyed, kommin. i Fröskog sed. 42.
translated: Lundgren, Gudmar Fredrik, Curate, Fröskog, b. 23/6/10 in Högbo, Gävleb. 1st child of former parish priest Johan L. and Signe Holmquist. Married in 1940 to Gunborg Ubrant. Children: Gudmar, b. 1940, Ulf, b. 1943, Torbjörn, b. 1946. — Completed secondary school in Karlstad in 1931, theological studies in 1933, theological bachelor's degree, practical theological examination, and ordained as a priest in the Karlstad diocese in 1937. Previously served as curate in Köla and Nyed, and has been a curate in Fröskog since 1942.
